group of people playing

00:01:19.570 --> 00:01:22.120
games on any platform ever.

00:01:22.120 --> 00:01:24.409
And then finally what that
translates then to you--

00:01:24.409 --> 00:01:26.200
last week we announced
that we had paid out

00:01:26.200 --> 00:01:28.730
more than $7 billion to
developers over the past 12

00:01:28.730 --> 00:01:29.520
months.

00:01:29.520 --> 00:01:31.865
So there's a very clear
commercial opportunity

00:01:31.865 --> 00:01:32.740
for developers today.

00:01:32.740 --> 00:01:36.480
And that number keeps
rising and rising.

00:01:36.480 --> 00:01:38.950
